{% comment %} TSQ Product Page — Notes Pyramid, What People Say, FAQ {% endcomment %}

{%- liquid
  assign top_notes    = product.metafields.tsq.top_notes.value    | default: ''
  assign heart_notes  = product.metafields.tsq.heart_notes.value  | default: ''
  assign base_notes   = product.metafields.tsq.base_notes.value   | default: ''
  assign reviews_json = product.metafields.tsq.reviews.value
-%}

{% comment %} ── FRAGRANCE NOTES PYRAMID ── {% endcomment %}
{% if top_notes != '' or heart_notes != '' or base_notes != '' %}
<div class="tsq-notes" style="max-width:var(--page-width,1280px);margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;">
  <p class="tsq-notes__title">✦ Fragrance Notes</p>
  <div class="tsq-notes__pyramid">

    <div class="tsq-notes__tier">
      <span class="tsq-notes__tier-icon">🍋</span>
      <p class="tsq-notes__tier-name">Top Notes</p>
      <div class="tsq-notes__bubbles">
        {% assign top_list = top_notes | split: ',' %}
        {% for note in top_list %}
          {% if note != '' %}
            <span class="tsq-notes__bubble">{{ note | strip }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tsq-notes__tier">
      <span class="tsq-notes__tier-icon">🌹</span>
      <p class="tsq-notes__tier-name">Heart Notes</p>
      <div class="tsq-notes__bubbles">
        {% assign heart_list = heart_notes | split: ',' %}
        {% for note in heart_list %}
          {% if note != '' %}
            <span class="tsq-notes__bubble">{{ note | strip }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tsq-notes__tier">
      <span class="tsq-notes__tier-icon">🪵</span>
      <p class="tsq-notes__tier-name">Base Notes</p>
      <div class="tsq-notes__bubbles">
        {% assign base_list = base_notes | split: ',' %}
        {% for note in base_list %}
          {% if note != '' %}
            <span class="tsq-notes__bubble">{{ note | strip }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% comment %} ── WHAT PEOPLE SAY ── {% endcomment %}
{% if reviews_json %}
<div class="tsq-reviews" style="max-width:var(--page-width,1280px);margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;">
  <h3 class="tsq-reviews__heading">What People Say</h3>
  <p class="tsq-reviews__sub">Community reviews from fragrance enthusiasts</p>
  <div class="tsq-reviews__grid">
    {% for review in reviews_json %}
      <div class="tsq-review-card">
        <div class="tsq-review-card__stars">
          {% assign stars = review.rating | default: 5 | round %}
          {% if stars < 4 %}{% assign stars = 4 %}{% endif %}
          {% for i in (1..stars) %}★{% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% if review.title != blank %}<p class="tsq-review-card__title">{{ review.title }}</p>{% endif %}
        <p class="tsq-review-card__text">"{{ review.body }}"</p>
        <span class="tsq-review-card__author">— {{ review.author }}{% if review.country %}, {{ review.country }}{% endif %}</span>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% comment %} ── FAQ ── {% endcomment %}
{%- liquid
  assign family = ''
  for tag in product.tags
    assign t = tag | downcase
    if t contains 'floral' or t contains 'rose'
      assign family = 'floral'
    elsif t contains 'oud'
      assign family = 'oud'
    elsif t contains 'fresh' or t contains 'aquatic' or t contains 'citrus'
      assign family = 'fresh'
    elsif t contains 'oriental' or t contains 'amber' or t contains 'spice'
      assign family = 'oriental'
    elsif t contains 'woody' or t contains 'wood' or t contains 'earthy'
      assign family = 'woody'
    elsif t contains 'gourmand' or t contains 'sweet' or t contains 'vanilla'
      assign family = 'gourmand'
    elsif t contains 'musk'
      assign family = 'musk'
    endif
  endfor
-%}

<div class="tsq-faq" style="max-width:var(--page-width,1280px);margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;">
  <h3 class="tsq-faq__title">Questions & Answers</h3>

  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      What is a decant?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">A decant is a small measured amount of fragrance drawn from the original bottle and transferred into a travel-friendly atomiser. You get the exact same juice as a full bottle — perfect for testing before committing.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      Is this a genuine {{ product.vendor }} fragrance?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Yes, 100%. Every fragrance we stock is sourced directly from authorised distributors. We do not deal in imitations, inspired-by versions, or grey-market product. What you receive is exactly the same fragrance as purchasing a full bottle.</div>
  </div>

  {% if family == 'oud' or family == 'oriental' %}
  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      This fragrance contains oud — how strong is it?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Oud-based fragrances tend to be rich, long-lasting, and project well. We recommend starting with 1–2 sprays if you're new to oud. A decant is an ideal way to live with the scent for a few days before committing to a full bottle.</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if family == 'floral' %}
  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      Is this fragrance suitable for daytime wear?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Floral fragrances are among the most versatile. This one works beautifully during the day and transitions elegantly into evening. Light and luminous, it suits warmer weather especially well.</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if family == 'fresh' %}
  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      How long does this fresh fragrance last?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Fresh and aquatic fragrances are designed for presence, not longevity. Expect 4–6 hours of projection. Applying to pulse points and moisturised skin significantly extends performance. A light reapplication midday is perfectly normal.</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {% if family == 'gourmand' %}
  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      Is this fragrance too sweet for everyday wear?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Gourmand fragrances walk a careful line — this one leans more sophisticated than sugary. The sweetness is balanced by resinous and woody base notes, making it wearable well beyond special occasions. A decant is the perfect way to decide if the sweetness level suits you.</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      How should I store my decant?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Keep away from direct sunlight, heat, and humidity. A cool, dark drawer or cabinet is ideal. Properly stored, your decant will remain in perfect condition for years.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      What sizes are available?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Decants are available in 3ml, 5ml, and 10ml. Select your preferred size using the size selector above. Larger sizes offer better value per ml.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tsq-faq__item">
    <button class="tsq-faq__question" onclick="tsqFaq(this)">
      Can I buy this as a gift?
      <span class="tsq-faq__icon">+</span>
    </button>
    <div class="tsq-faq__answer">Absolutely. Our packaging is presentation-quality and our decants make excellent gifts for fragrance lovers. If you'd like a personalised note included, add it in the order notes at checkout.</div>
  </div>

</div>
